<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .left {
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            float: left;
        }

        .right > div {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .content {
            position: absolute;
            top:407px;
            font-family: "NotoSans-Regular";
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-stretch: normal;
            line-height: normal;
            letter-spacing: -0.4px;
            color: #222222;
        }
        .blue {
            color: blue;
        }
        
        
        .right {
            float: right;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .tag {
            width: 138px;
            height: 83px;
            font-family: 'NotoSans-Black', sans-serif;
            font-size: 56px;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-style: normal;
            font-stretch: normal;
            line-height: normal;
            letter-spacing: -1.1px;
            color: #222222;
        }

        .reBtn {
            width: 124px;
            height: 33px;
            font-family: "NotoSans-Regular";
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-stretch: normal;
            line-height: normal;
            letter-spacing: -0.4px;
            color: #a7a7a7;
        }

        .rediv {
            position: absolute;
            top:157px;
        }

        #actionBtn {
            width: 274px;
            height: 72px;
            border-radius: 42px;
            border-width: 0px;
            box-shadow: 8px 10px 12px 0 rgba(63, 51, 255, 0.3);
            background-color: #3f33ff;

            font-family: "NotoSans-Regular";
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-style: normal;
            font-stretch: normal;
            line-height: normal;
            letter-spacing: -0.4px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .big_box {
            overflow: auto;
            width: 85%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .small_box {
            position: relative;
            top: 157px; 
            float: left;
            text-align: center;
            width: 45%;
            max-height: 200px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-width: 2px;
            border-color: #3f33ff;
            border-style: solid;
            margin: 5px;

            font-family: 'NotoSans-Regular', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: -0.32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #3f33ff;

        }
        
        .small_box>.title {
            font-family: 'NotoSans-Black', sans-serif;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -0.7px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #3f33ff;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="left">
        <div class="big_box">
            <%= datas %>
            <div class="small_box"> 
                <br><br>
                <span class="title">#바다스타그램</span>
                <br>
                최근 ‘바다스타그램’태그가 <br>포함된 게시글 2,310개
                <br><br><br>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="right">
        <div>
            <div class="rediv">
                <img src="/images/back.svg" alt="" width="22" height="22">
                <span class="reBtn">&nbsp;다시 검색하기</span>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                총 65개의 태그를 분석해
                <br>
                <span class="tag">'바다'</span><br>
                와 관련있는 인스타그램 태그를 찾았습니다. 
                <br><br>
                쓸만한 태그를 선택해서 클립보드에 복사하세요.
                <br>
                <br>
                <button id="actionBtn">태그 전부 복사</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>